http://www.food.gov.uk/news/newsarchive/2011/nov/botulismwarn.
3. Health Protection Scotland (HPS). Public urged to be aware of
botulism symptoms. HPS: Glasgow. 11 November 2011. Available from:
http://www.hps.scot.nhs.uk/news/SPdetail.aspx?id=435.
